PrecisAmendments to Order in Council P.C. 1995-325 which authorize the Canadian Food Inspection Agency, instead of the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food, to prescribe, BY ORDER, the fees or charges to be paid for a service or the use of a facility provided by the Agency or for the issuance of a licence, permit or other authorization.
